K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-040:136b-0: @136b pha rol tu phyin pa drug gi snying po'i gzungs /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-040:136b-1: 'phags pa yum shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-040:136b-9: d'a na p'a ra mi t'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-040:136b-10: sh'i la p'a ra mi t'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-040:136b-13: dhy'a na p'a ra mi t'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-040:136b-16: 'di bzung bas pha rol tu phyin pa drug gzung bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-040:136b-17: stong pa nyid yid la byas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-040:136b-18: rtag tu bzlas brjod byas na chos thams cad kyi mdo dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-040:136b-20: mtshams med pa lnga byang bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-096-040:137a-2: pha rol tu phyin pa drug gi snying po rdzogs so ////
